 trail shirts. The<a href=\"https://www.ornotbike.com/products/uv-trail-shirt-mcnally-sketches?variant=44947074679076\" target=\"_blank\"> “Sketchy”</a> design combines ten years’ worth of sketches and brings them to life, showcasing scenes from San Francisco, taco stops, airport doodles, and maybe even a few misspellings (don’t worry, we can’t spell either). In the second design, <a href=\"https://www.ornotbike.com/products/uv-trail-shirt-mcnally-poppy?variant=44947108004132\" target=\"_blank\">“Poison Poppies”</a>, Chris pays homage to California’s most iconic plants – Poison Oak and Poppies – minus the pesky itchiness. Both shirts capture Chris’s unique watercolor vibes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/Ornot_UV_Trail_Shirt_McNally_Sketchy_01-scaled.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/20