0&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Shirt-W_22034_0048.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en/shop/specialized-fjllrven-exchange/c/fjallravencollection\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized + Fjällräven Exchange Spring ’23</a></h3>\n<p>Adventure doesn’t have to be far-flung in distant lands or require months of planning in advance. Nature is at the end of a train ride, on the edge of town, or even just around the corner. From next-level on-bike storage solutions and bags to technical apparel and accessories, this exchange is based on the unfailing belief that the more people who discover the joy that comes from being in nature, the more the world will benefit. Fjällräven and Specialized. Sweden and California. Hiking and biking. Discover new trails and perspectives, where the air is fresh and the mind is clear.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Field-Suit_22031_22032_0104.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Field-Suit_22031_22032_0104.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Field-Suit_22031_22032_0104.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/S_F-Sun-Field-Suit_22031_