://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX6_PNK-BLU_Sp.Ed_._004-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX6_PNK-BLU_Sp.Ed_._004-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX6_PNK-BLU_Sp.Ed_._004-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX6_PNK-BLU_Sp.Ed_._004-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX6_PNK-BLU_Sp.Ed_._004-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/RX8_Wine_Sp.Ed_._008-3000x3000-2567b33-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://ride.shimano.com/collections/gravel-adventure?gclid=CjwKCAjwx_eiBhBGEiwA15gLNzyJ5JEESZbp5rHy90Bsf8cu0_tEXND38dFVEWLSqcK6ZTql7uZhjBoCkvsQAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\">Shimano Flint Hills Edition RX8 and RX6 Gravel Shoes</a></h3>\n<p><strong>RX8 Twilight Gravel Shoes</strong> $275<br />\nSaluting the rolling hills and open range roads of the Flint Hills, the RX8 Twilight gravel shoes are made for pushing boundaries and searching for what you have deep inside. The new Twilight gravel shoes blend the performance features and efficiency of the much-loved RX8 gravel race shoe with the purple evening glow as night descends on the tallgrass prairie.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BOA Li2 dial</li>\n<li>Synthetic leather upper</li>\n<li>Stiff carbon composite sole</li>\n<li>Scratch resistant TPU outsole</li>\n<li>Refined toe box fit</li>\n<li>Vivid inkjet-printed graphics</li>\n<li>Weight: 268 grams (size 42)</li>\n<li>US Regular Sizes: 38, 39, 40, 41, 42-45(half sizes), 46</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The RX6 Moonlight</strong> $180</p>\n<p>Riding through sunset into the night, Shimano’s RX6 Moonlight gravel shoes celebrate the journey riders take each June in the tallgrass prairies of Kansas. Showcasing the sky’s transformation from day to night as the prairie clouds darken and night awakens, the RX6 Moonlight gravel shoes salute the adventure ahead and those riders ready to tackle the challenge of evening’s darkness.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BOA L6 dial</li>\n<li>Stiff carbon-reinforced outsole</li>\n<li>Wider outsole for extra stability</li>\n<li>Vivid inkjet-printed graphics</li>\n<li>Weight: 274 grams (size 42)</li>\n<li>US Regular Sizes: 38-46 whole sizes only</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1033\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?w=1033&amp;quality=75 1033w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?resize=1024,1983&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?resize=768,1487&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?resize=700,1355&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS.jpg?resize=793,1536&amp;quality=75 793w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1033\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?w=1033&amp;quality=75 1033w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?resize=1024,1983&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?resize=768,1487&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?resize=700,1355&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-3.jpg?resize=793,1536&amp;quality=75 793w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1033\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?w=1033&amp;quality=75 1033w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?resize=1024,1983&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?resize=768,1487&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?resize=700,1355&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/ABUS-2.jpg?resize=793,1536&amp;quality=75 793w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://originm.abus.com/usa/Products/Bicycle-locks/Special-Locks/Combiflex-TravelGuard-black\" target=\"_blank\">ABUS CombiFlex TravelGuard Lock</a>  $34.99</h3>\n<p>Flexible, reliable, and always at hand. The Combiflex TravelGuard is the perfect safeguard for your helmet or backpack or bike while you are out and about and dont want to bring a heavy U-lock. This will stop opportunistic thieves, and you can enjoy your break with peace of mind. Simply hanging your helmet on the handlebar without securing it or leaving your backpack unattended shouldn’t even be considered. ABUS makes this essential protection simple.</p>\n<p>The Combiflex TravelGuard can quickly and reliably lock helmets, bags, and bikes thanks to its lightweight and minimalistic design. Ideal for short stops on the commute and can be stowed in most pockets, bags, or even jersey pockets. Whether at the cafe or running errands, it’s an uncomplicated way to protect your property against theft. An extra solid steel core and a 3-digit opening code provide protection and peace of mind. The numeric code can be set and changed individually. The 45cm (18in) long cable forms a lashing loop, the length of which can be freely adjusted. The flexible and versatile design allows for a wide range of uses to offer peace of mind while away from your bike!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cable protection with extra solid steel core</li>\n<li>3-Digit Code means there are no keys to lose</li>\n<li>Cable lock with releasable locking mechanism</li>\n<li>Small and lightweight, fits well in pants or jersey pocket (80g)</li>\n<li>Available in Red, Yellow, and Black</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://originm.abus.com/usa/Products/Bicycle-locks/Special-Locks/Combiflex-TravelGuard-black\" target=\"_blank\">ABUS</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/nfg-bottom-image-5-bucks-gravel-2023-2600-10-scaled-1.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://sierratrails.networkforgood.com/projects/193359-five-bucks-a-foot-gravel-for-connected-communities\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship Launches 2023 “5 Bucks a Foot”</a></h3>\n<p>The Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship, originators of the famous 5 Bucks a Foot fundraiser, returns with its first-ever gravel-bike campaign, with all proceeds benefiting the organization’s visionary Connected Communities Project and its mission to use trails as a tool to revitalize rural mountain communities.</p>\n<p>In this 5 Bucks A Foot, one lucky winner will take home a decked-out full-carbon Cervélo Aspero-5 gravel bike, valued at $7,500. As in the past, each $5 donation (the average cost per foot of building a trail) nets one entry—the more feet purchased, the more chances to take home the Áspero-5. The campaign closes at 9 a.m. on June 4, and the winner will be able to select the frame size of their choice: 48, 51, 54, 56, 58 or 61.</p>\n<p>Head over to <a href=\"https://sierratrails.networkforgood.com/projects/193359-five-bucks-a-foot-gravel-for-connected-communities\" target=\"_blank\">SBTS to donate</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G94dxRgZ6J0\" target=\"_blank\">Hannah Barnes – Motherhood, Mountain Biking, &amp; Instilling a Love of Riding</a></h3>\n<p>This Mother’s Day, Hannah Barnes shares an inside look at her home life, as well as her candid thoughts on motherhood, the importance of presence, her love and history with mountain bikes, and fostering a love for the outdoors in the next generation of little riders.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/DSC03247-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><i>Photo via <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hailey.m.moore/\" target=\"_blank\">@hailey.m.moore</a></i></p>\n<p><i></i>Hailey Moore and Tony Krupicka were out on the Rapha Yomp Rally last week, which traversed 375 miles from Santa Barbara to Los Angeles. It looked BURLY, yet strikingly beautiful.</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-ornot-x-chris-mcnally-trail-shirts-specialized-fjallraven-exchange-shimano-flint-hills-shoes-abus-travelguard-five-bucks-a-foot-and-motherhood-and-mountain-biking/\">Radar Roundup: Ornot X Chris McNally Trail Shirts, Specialized + Fjällräven Exchange, Shimano Flint Hills Shoes, Abus TravelGuard, Five Bucks a Foot, and Motherhood and Mountain Biking</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"Josh Weinberg","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"dc4baa5894d8bfe1f3a33c7b95e1f857d8c4c8307f97793d8e535d9c2ae771ca","category":"Cycling"}